data.description: Discover luxury living in this stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home with an office located on a large corner lot with RV parking. Boasting over 2500 sq ft, this split-wing home is adorned with solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. The open great room, adorned with tile floors, welcomes you with a cozy fireplace and transitions seamlessly to a dining room area and chef's kitchen. The kitchen is a culinary haven with custom wood cabinets, granite countertops, a large granite island with seating, and a charming breakfast area. The office has built-in shelves and offers versatility, dedicated workspace or a potential 4th bedroom. The master suite is a retreat, featuring a walk-in closet, plush carpet, and a spa-like bathroom. A barn door adds a touch of elegance, separating the bathroom with dual sinks and a vanity, a separate soaking tub, and a spacious walk-in shower.  The backyard is perfect for entertaining, complete with a covered patio and ample space for a future pool. Call today to see!
